  "instructions": [
    "Place the buttermilk in a shallow dish and add ground cumin, coriander, turmeric powder, salt, crushed garlic clove, onion, and chopped pistachios. Mix well to combine.",
    "Sous-vide the mixture at 160\u00b0F for about 3 hours to create a crispy texture without oil.",
    "Once sous-vived, remove from the bag and mix thoroughly with your hands until fully combined.",
    "Serve immediately as a snack or hangover cure."
